msgid ""
"The regular expression for capturing the counterpart amount appears to be "
"incorrectly formatted.\n"
"Please make sure that the part of the regex capturing the amount (in "
"parentheses) cannot capture an empty value (usually by an incorrect use of ? "
"or *) or any value with no digit. For example: BRT: ([\\d,.]+)."
msgstr ""
"ຮູບແບບ Regular expression ສຳລັບການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນຈຳນວນເງິນກົງກັນຂ້າມເບິ່ງຄືວ່າຈະບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າພາກສ່ວນຂອງ regex ທີ່ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນຈຳນວນເງິນ (ໃນວົງເລັບ) ບໍ່ສາມາດດຶງຄ່າຫວ່າງໄດ້ "
"ຫຼື ຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ມີຕົວເລກ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: BRT: ([\\d,.]+)."

#. module: account_accountant
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_accountant/models/account_reconcile_model_line.py:0
msgid ""
"The regular expression for capturing the counterpart amount appears to be "
"incorrectly formatted.\n"
"Please make sure that the part of the regex capturing the amount is the "
"first (or only) one in parentheses, for example: BRT: ([\\d,.]+)."
msgstr ""
"ຮູບແບບ Regular expression ສຳລັບການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນຈຳນວນເງິນກົງກັນຂ້າມເບິ່ງຄືວ່າຈະບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າພາກສ່ວນຂອງ regex ທີ່ດຶງຂໍ້ມູນຈຳນວນເງິນນັ້ນຢູ່ໃນວົງເລັບທຳອິດ (ຫຼື ອັນດຽວ), ຕົວ"
"ຢ່າງ: BRT: ([\\d,.]+)."

